LB304 LB304
DLM - 02/10/2026 DLM - 02/10/2026
1 contract shall be entered into as provided in section 68-1719. If
2 assistance is requested for only the child or children in such a family,
3 such children shall be eligible after consideration of the family's
4 income and if (i) the family cooperates in pursuing child support and
5 (ii) the minor children of the family regularly attend school.
6 Sec. 3. Original sections 68-1206 and 68-1724, Revised Statutes
7 Cumulative Supplement, 2024, are repealed.
